 SEMINAR

 March 18 at Rani Birla Girls? College; 10.30 am - 5 pm: UGC-sponsored inter-disciplinary seminar on Gendered Violence and Atrocities against Women. 

 March 18 at Landmark; Lord Sinha Road; 7.30 pm: Emami Landmark Store presents a panel discussion, Will cricket better India-Pakistan relations? Panelists include Raju Mukherjee, Rameez Raja, Ayaz Menon, Sharda Ugra and Rahul Bhattacharya. The discussion is being held to mark the launch of the book, Pundits from Pakistan. 

