 EXHIBITION

 Till March 19 at Genesis Art Gallery, 8B Middleton Street: Sundari Silks presents an exhibition of silk and cotton sarees of south India. 

 Till March 19 at 89 Elliot Road; 10 am - 5 pm: All Bengal Women?s Union presents a spring sale of handicrafts, household linen and snacks, the proceeds for which will be used for the development of the under-privileged. 

